# üé® iOS-like Design Standard

**Core Philosophy:** Clean, Solid, Performant. Function > Fashion.
**Target:** Low-end devices (UMKM market) with premium feel.

---

## üì± Mobile-First Standards

- **Touch Targets:** Minimum 44x44px
- **Loading States:** Always show skeleton or spinner
- **Empty States:** Illustrations + helpful message
- **Images:** `loading="lazy"` + proper sizing

## üéØ Design Principles

### 1. **Clean Solid Design** (No Fake Glass)
- **Navbar/Footer:** `bg-white border-b border-slate-200 shadow-sm`
- **Cards:** `bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl shadow-sm`
- **Modals:** `bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-slate-200`
- **Rule:** Solid backgrounds + crisp borders + subtle shadows

**Available Components:**
- `FormInput` - Text input with icon support
- `FormSelect` - Dropdown selector
- `FormTextarea` - Multi-line text
- `FormNumberInput` - Number with +/- controls
- `FormCheckbox` - Checkbox with description
- badge
- basemodal
- alerts
- dialog

### 2. **Motion (Strategic Use)**
Keep `motion-v` for high-impact moments:
- ‚úÖ Page transitions: `motion-v preset-fade`
- ‚úÖ Modals: `motion-v preset-slide-up`
- ‚úÖ Button press: `:whileTap="{ scale: 0.97 }"`
- ‚ùå Long lists (use CSS `transition-all duration-200` instead)

**Spring Config:** `{ stiffness: 300, damping: 28 }`

### 3. **Press Feedback** (Essential)
All interactive elements must respond:
```vue
<!-- Buttons -->
<button class="... active:scale-97 transition-transform">

<!-- Primary Actions -->
<button class="bg-emerald-500 hover:bg-emerald-600 shadow-sm shadow-emerald-500/10">

<!-- Cards (Desktop) -->
<div class="hover:scale-101 transition-transform">
```

### 4. **Haptic Feedback**
```ts
haptics.light()   // Tap, switch
haptics.medium()  // Success, submit
haptics.heavy()   // Delete, error
```

### 5. **Typography**
- **Font:** System Sans (0ms load)
- **Hierarchy:** `text-slate-900` (primary) / `text-slate-500` (secondary)
- **Labels:** `text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase text-slate-600`
- **Whitespace:** Generous padding (`p-4`, `p-6`)

